  "texts": [
    "Data for the auditory midbrain of the 17th participant is missing because the MRI-slab did not cover the midbrain of the participant.",
    "All p-values were corrected for 6 comparisons independently for each participant.",
    "ns: not significant; *: p < 0.05; **: p < 0.01; ***: p < 0.001; ****: p < 0.0001.",
    "IC: inferior colliculus (auditory midbrain); MGB: medial geniculate body (auditory thalamus); PAC: auditory cortex.",
    "aPE: absence prediction error.Figure 1:1Figure1: Experimental design and hypotheses."
